Package client.view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardView
    A view to display the game map, the players counters and get which node the users click on.
    ChatEventView
    A view to display the game log.
    ChatView
    A view for displaying a button to toggle between showing and hiding the game log.
    Formatter
    A class to centralise the styling of frequently used components and store the colours.
    GameView
    A view to display the board, players information and previous moves.
    ListView
    A view to display a List of RouteViews.
    MenuBar
    A view to hold the views that make up the menu bar.
    NotifyView
    A view to display a messages to the players.
    PlayerTicketView
    A view to display the players tickets.
    RouteView
    A view to display a sequence of Moves.
    SetUpView
    A view to allow players to set up a new game or load an existing one.
    TimerView
    A view to display a countdown timer.
